<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">During Your Appointment</h3>

<div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <p class="mb-4">
    With 60% of women waxing or shaving, bikini waxing has become a common practice. However, it's perfectly normal to feel nervous if it's your first time. The process will depend on the type of wax used and the areas you want to target. Waxing is a quick and easy procedure that only takes a few minutes.
  </p>
