    You'll lie comfortably on a salon bed to give our esthetician access to the area. Depending on how much hair you want to remove, you may or may not have to remove your underwear. Waxing along the panty line is a popular practice to get rid of visible hair. We call this service Bikini Line.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Our esthetician will begin by cleansing the area before applying a protective oil barrier. This product will provide a thin layer of protection to the skin. Next, our esthetician will apply melted wax to the area using a clean wax stick and then disposing of it promptly. She may lay more than one strip allowing the previous strips to dry.
  </p>
  <p>
